*memwatch-0.3.0-r1 (13 Jun 2016)

  13 Jun 2016; Patrice Clement <monsieurp@gentoo.org>
  +memwatch-0.3.0-r1.ebuild:
  Remove default curses module.

  The CMake curses module shipped with memwatch is buddy and prevents CMake
  from
  performing a proper linking against ncurses. To work around this issue,
  remove
  it so that CMake can find the correct ncurses library installed on the
  system
  and link the resulting memwatch binary correctly against it.

  Gentoo-Bug: https://bugs.gentoo.org/585802

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.28

